e.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amanda-seyfried">阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-tonight-show-starring-jimmy-fallon"><em>吉米·法伦（Jimmy Fallon）主演的《今晚秀》（Tonight Show）</em></a>上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）</a>的标志性1971年《加利福尼亚》（California&#39;）的简短封面 - 在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/joni-mitchells-court-and-spark-at-50-3577635">乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）的“法庭和火花”（Spark）在50岁：“她是我们这一代酷姨妈的每个人”</a></strong></li></ul><p>塞耶弗里德（Seyfried）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-fallon">法伦（Fallon）</a>出现在<em>《今晚节目》（The Tonight Show</em> ）的最新一集中，以宣传她即将上映的电视节目<em>《长河》（Long Bright River）</em> ，启动了他们谈论她的音乐才华的谈话，包括她在诸如<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/mamma-mia"><em>妈妈米娅（Mamma Mia）之类的音乐电影中的表演！</em></a>和<em>爱情的玛索</em>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3843944" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843944" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843944" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843944" class="wp-caption-text">阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）。图片来源：Gerald Matzka/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及她的音乐才华时，塞弗里德透露，她在19次大流行期间学会了如何扮演扬琴。法伦（Fallon）挥舞着一个扬琴之后，塞弗里德（Seyfried）分享说，她想在乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）备受喜爱的“蓝色”专辑中播放“加利福尼亚”。</p><p> “她在扬琴上写了很多蓝色专辑中的歌曲，当世界停下来时，我从那个专辑中学到了很多东西，”塞弗里德在发起《加利福尼亚&#39;的第一节经文和合唱》之前说。</p><p>在下面查看她的封面。 </p><p><iframe title="阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）唱歌并扮演扬声器，说萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）应该加入妈妈米亚（Mamma Mia）！ 3铸件" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ly0kgS2UioA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>情节播出并在社交媒体上分享了演出的片段之后，观众们对她的表演感到惊讶，此后开始倡导她在传记片中扮演米切尔。</p><p>在她的几个支持者中，请参见下面的Instagram帖子的评论部分 - 包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jameela-jamil-on-how-she-ruined-glastonbury-for-coldplay-superfan-benedict-cumberbatch-3838706">Jameela Jamil</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/regina-spektor">Regina Spektor</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">Gwen Stefani</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maya-hawke">Maya Hawke</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-tedder">Ryan Tedder</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlie-puth">Charlie Puth</a> ，Matt Bomer，Sheryl Bomer， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">Sheryl Crow</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-paul">Aaron Paul</a>和Kate Hudson。贾米尔写道：“得到。那。传记片。女孩。”</p><p>其他评论者支持她的观点，写道：“天哪。这就是她的声音的目的。很想看到她扮演年轻的乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）。</p><p>在下面查看更多评论和反应。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGzZTi7upV-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 5