 “他妈的杰夫·贝佐斯”：邪教恐怖导演奥斯古德·珀金斯永远不会导演詹姆斯·邦德电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/fuck-jeff-bezos-cult-horror-director-osgood-perkins-would-never-direct-james-bond-film-3843909?ut m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = fuck-jeff-bezos-bezos-cult-horror-director-osgood-osgood-perkins-perkins-perkins-ward-never-derver-direct-direct-direct-james-bond-filmChris Edwards Wed, 05 Mar 2025 21:26:29 +0000 Film NewsNewsAmazon PrimeAmazon Prime Video https://www.nme.com/?p=3843909 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·邦德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他想制作一部“星球大战”电影</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fuck-jeff-bezos-cult-horror-director-osgood-perkins-would-never-direct-james-bond-film-3843909">“ Fuck Jeff Bezos”：邪教恐怖导演Osgood Perkins永远不会导演James Bond电影</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·邦德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bond-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><em>猴子</em>导演奥斯古德·珀金斯（Osgood Perkins）说，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amazon">亚马逊</a>已收购了这家专营权，因此他不想制作<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/james-bond">詹姆斯·邦德（James Bond）的</a>电影。</p><p>在最近的<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/movies/comments/1izhqr1/hey_rmovies_im_osgood_perkins_writer_and_director/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit AMA</a>中，恐怖导演被粉丝询问：“您愿意执导邦德电影/三部曲吗？如果是这样，您会把谁当作您的Bond版本？”</p><p>珀金斯简单地回答：“不，因为他妈的杰夫·贝佐斯（Jeff Bezos）。”</p><p>这是在亿万富翁贝佐斯（Bezos）以前似乎公开支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的亿万富翁</a>之后，他写道，参加特朗普在2025年的第二次就职典礼是一种“荣誉”。“很高兴合作地加速创新和增强美国经济，”贝佐斯当时评论说。</p><p>尽管珀金斯因贝佐斯（Bezos）排除了邦德（Bond）的排除，但他确实透露了他很乐意加入的另一个标志性特许经营权 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>星球大战</em></a>。</p><p>珀金斯写道，他的理想电影，如果预算不是对象，那将是“达斯·维达（Darth Vader）的梦想和噩梦，如短篇小说。” </p><figure id="attachment_3774773" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774773" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774773" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty.jpg" alt="奥斯古德·珀金斯（Osgood Perkins）" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/OsgoodPerkins-Longlegs-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774773" class="wp-caption-text">奥斯古德·珀金斯（Osgood Perkins）拒绝执导詹姆斯·邦德（James Bond）的电影。学分：JC Olivera/Getty图像霓虹灯</figcaption></figure><p>导演名单上的其他项目包括“完全构成了一个关于真实人的传记片，一个新的弗洛伊德人西方，以及一部电影，讲述了一个著名的人，他去世了，他们在年轻人和来世的经历。”</p><p>珀金斯继续解释说，他的视觉风格受到他最喜欢的电影的影响。 “我试图做我喜欢的东西。我不知道该怎么说。”他写道。 “这最终意味着从复制自己的偶像和影响力开始，”从大卫·林奇（David Lynch）到阿尔弗雷德·希区柯克（Alfred Hitchcock）和斯坦利·库布里克（Stanley Kubrick）。</p><p>在亚马逊收购詹姆斯·邦德（James Bond）之后，许多<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-bond-fans-furious-about-amazon-takeover-theyre-going-to-absolutely-ruin-it-3840357">粉丝表示担心，如果没有迈克尔·威尔逊（Michael G. Wilson）和芭芭拉·布罗科利（Barbara Broccoli）的创造性影响，那么心爱的特许经营将被“毁了”</a> 。</p><p>没有关于下一部詹姆斯·邦德电影的正式宣布，最后是丹尼尔·克雷格（Daniel Craig）在2021年<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/no-time-to-die"><em>没有时间死亡的</em></a>告别。</p><p>下一个007的铸造目前也在播出，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-taylor-johnson">亚伦·泰勒·约翰逊（Aaron Taylor-Johnson）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/henry-cavill">亨利·卡维尔（Henry Cavill）</a>等人经常与该角色联系在一起。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fuck-jeff-bezos-cult-horror-director-osgood-perkins-would-never-direct-james-bond-film-3843909">“ Fuck Jeff Bezos”：邪教恐怖导演Osgood Perkins永远不会导演James Bond电影</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
戈迪（Goldie https://www.nme.com/news/music/goldie-returns-as-rufige-kru-kru-to-share-new-new-single-still-th-------------------------------------- and-new-same-with-annouse-annouse-album-album-alpha-alpha-alpha-amega-omega-3843905?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = goldie-returns-as-as-rufige-kru-kru-kru-kru-kru-to-share new-new single-new-new-same-same-same-with-casisdead and announce-ancounce-album-album-alpha-omegaEmma Wilkes Wed, 05 Mar 2025 21:24:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3843905 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Goldie和Sumpotive。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我想创建一些绝对代表这首音乐的内容……以及接下来要去的地方”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/goldie-returns-as-rufige-kru-to-share-new-single-still-the-same-with-casisdead-and-announce-album-alpha-omega-3843905">戈尔迪（Post Goldie）作为鲁菲格·克鲁（Rufige Kru）返回，与Casisdead共享新单曲“仍然相同”，并宣布专辑“ Alpha Omega”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Goldie和Sumpotive。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/goldie-rufige-kru-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/goldie">Goldie</a>的BreakBeat Alter Ego Rufige Kru卷土重来，与Casisdead分享了新单曲“ Still Same”，并宣布了一张新专辑“ Alpha Omega”。</p><p>这部新单曲是在粉丝向Casisdead提出的多年要求以“ N&#39;低音曲目”的说唱之后的多年要求。这是他备受赞誉的2023专辑“著名last Wists”以来的第一个发行。该曲目是由Goldie和Subsotive生产的。</p><p>同时，由Elliott Gonzo执导的“仍然相同”的音乐视频以Goldie为AI霸王，被Vigilante Casisdead追捕。</p><p>奇闻趣事在新闻稿中说：“与这些传奇人物合作是一种巨大的荣幸。” “我得到的自由和信任意味着我可以真正地将新技术的可能性与动画和虚拟制作结合在一起。对我的联合导演Buse Simon的大声喊叫，以帮助将这些新世界栩栩如生。”</p><p>在下面查看： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Goldie展示Rufige Kru-仍然相同（壮举。Casisdead）[官方视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mxuA4Xmvuw8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “ Alpha Omega”将于5月16日通过伦敦唱片发布。</p><p>关于专辑的主题，戈迪说：“这是一个重塑。我们回到了来源，并从那里推断了。我想创建一些绝对代表这种音乐的内容……以及接下来要去的地方。”</p><p>他补充说：“我已经与詹姆斯（Submotive）一起旅行了这场比赛的各个角度，现在他是Rufige Kru Echelon的强大合作伙伴….boss Levelz。</p><p> “我回到了我的根源。 “这对我来说是一件美丽的事情。我花了很多时间来磨练自己的手艺，发展这些概念，组装了所有这些时刻。但是，这种可能性的感觉 - 使我在早期的前进 - 仍然存在。我仍然对这种音乐以及那些几年前的音乐可以去的地方感到兴奋。唯一的限制是我的想象力。”</p><h3> <strong>“ Alpha Omega”的跟踪列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>&#39;alpha Omega&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Goldikus壮举。克利夫兰·沃特基斯</strong><br /><strong>“维吉尔”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;表达你的灵魂</strong><br /><strong>“沙堡”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;仍然是同样的壮举。 casisdead&#39;</strong><br /><strong>汞&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“暹罗鬼”</strong><br /> <strong>“秘密握手”</strong><br /> <strong>“精神”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;人和地方</strong><br /><strong>&#39;瓜尼兹&#39;</strong> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGqnrQGCu3T/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.